{"tid":731598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[QR Code支付贏晒] 澳門發現騙徒藉推薦清理軟件以二維碼盜用手機錢包款項","createTime":"2018-07-06T10:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T06:20:59.000Z","uid":51271,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"443938a13670232b58596fd6b2dcc0b1990057b9","tid":731598,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"澳門出現新型電話詐騙。司警透過網站公佈，近日收到市民舉報，指有網友推薦清理手機通訊軟件，清除在聊天平台長時間無互動，俗稱「殭屍粉」的朋友名單。<br />\n<br />\n當事主按指示將對方加為「好友」，並透過手機錢包支付了小額服務費，即時收到對方發出的二維碼，事主掃描並進行清理「殭屍粉」程序後，結果發現被對方盜用手機錢包內的存款，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n司警呼籲市民不要隨便掃描來歷不明的二維碼，避免手機被入侵或植入病毒，而導致個人訊息或銀行帳號等重要資料外洩，被不法分子利用犯案或騙取金錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405574-20180706.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405574-20180706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cx0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=888a1481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1405574-20180706.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=528779ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1405574-20180706.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4b41f6aebbcec4a36c7d604a94861a0a3bc457bf","tid":731598,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"We柒pay 支爆寶贏晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe78a370eef87c56b6db6f0bf588ad61979715b8","tid":731598,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n